Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}1924年 聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被死神碰了 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說到底誰更可怕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校每到聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會變裝地來 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿普麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學你也換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這麼說 我也沒衣服可以換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說 剛才塞西爾老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲 還沒好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這不就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在學校的聖誕派對上穿過的衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我雖然不過是個新來的幫傭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但塞西爾一定要兩個人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想跟妳一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿的…就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是玩偶服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裡 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟是用水晶珠子做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看吧 漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說血管都在閃閃發亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個莫非就是美獸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是流傳在我國的一個傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怪談嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是個童話故事更確切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很浪漫的故事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本國 有一隻化身為少女的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一隻兔子一直為她打雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子武藝超群 打跑了所有想得到怪物而接近她的惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子就這麼猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物也會劫富濟貧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而代理她施捨的就是兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物日漸受到人民的歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當權者也將得到她作為權力的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而日益加緊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當權者們終於殺死了想要保護怪物的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想 這樣一來就能得到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物也已經不在世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那隻兔子就是怪物的心臟 是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物和兔子實際上是一心同體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得心臟做得這麼華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件衣服給久城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你給維多利嘉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們翹首以待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我忘記阿普麗爾同學也喜歡久城同學了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西爾 妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想不想做美獸二代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已經換好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短髮妖精好可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是今天的變裝皇后了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.52,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,570)}窗邊聖歌綴薄倖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小甜餅馬上要跑出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉…妳是不是甜食吃太多胖了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區食草哺乳動物還敢囂張？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邊蕾絲飄飄下～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是陪妳去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是美獸傳奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裙子真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許摸我頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問妳啊 妳為啥想到這個點子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉的生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神一變成兔子也就沒那麼可怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會去跳舞吧 死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來為大家所畏懼的黑色死神也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色妖精也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那麼大家所有人的聖誕禮物已經裝在這棵樹上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家各取所需吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學 我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選這個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣做真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是妳媽媽考迪利亞女士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然把這麼貴重的東西隨便給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不知道會被誰拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你是隨春而來的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正無論如何 你這個人肯定會讓大家先選禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大眾都盯著那些包裝精美內容豐富的去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下那些不起眼的小禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上黑白蕾絲會讓你聯想起某人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你必然會選這個盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 一切都是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會珍惜的 我會一直把它當傳家寶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 我也有禮物要給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等我一下 我給妳拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 我馬上拿給妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 雖然我懂是懂 但總還是不開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是金色妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是短髮妖精啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是金髮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為啥大家就不那麼叫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 我染髮去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要染成大紅大綠的聖誕色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊飾跟戒指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼覺得我們想到一塊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請問你是久城一彌同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是魯伯特國王陛下的手諭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿普麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個…給維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求妳了 阿普麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經採取措施 讓他國的商人和官員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及留學生先行回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐洲終於也要燃起久違的戰火了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 我國一貫以永久中立為政策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使世界發生巨變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國也應堅守本分 不被這股浪潮吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕就委任你了 羅傑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 正因為是亂世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街頭巷尾最近傳言甚多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所謂的傳言是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣略有耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據稱美獸再臨我國了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,26
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 這太野蠻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼事先沒有通知…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 我們會將你平安送回國內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝陛下的好意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果戰爭爆發 那我們就無法送你回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後數年內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將有一狂風暴雨席捲世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們尚且身輕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或會因這風暴而分離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻兔子是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的指示 我們奉的是國王陛下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就這樣分開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話待會說 中國人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群潛伏在地下的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部給我抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨蹭了 趁現在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼又碰上這種麻煩 你這人真令人頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡 路易吉你不是和賈可琳小姐一起出城了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 多虧了她我才成了有錢人家的養子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直待在深宅大院裡多拘謹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我偶爾跑出來重溫以前的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種生活也快到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟外面阿兵哥那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭快爆發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到剛才那些兔頭隊伍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊現在在鎮壓國內的危險分子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險分子是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於憂國憂民 拯救彷徨的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美獸據說會再次降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美獸嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些兔頭的口號就是「美獸所求即不義人之血」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那些人是渴望打仗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 組織不斷擴大中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有傳聞說他們想對現在軟弱的政府實行行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些怕人的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去維多利嘉那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得很不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要拆散你們這一對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一彌可以留在維多利嘉的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜託格雷維爾看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但警部他是靈異部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 他每次到緊要關頭都會挺身而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次肯定也能幫上你們的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布羅瓦警部就算那樣 看上去也是很擔心維多利嘉…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩義德跟伊梅爾達也走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回宿舍去吧 維多利嘉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是把這身衣服換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這吊墜真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學還真懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿點吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請蘇菲小姐做些熱湯來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨時隨地都會去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論何時都在妳身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說大話了 久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在明明…這麼想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說讓他逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓他落入了靈異部之手的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是落到我們手裡又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老蜥蜴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…該叫美獸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈異部用人之時終於也到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓那些人利用我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不妨就在這裡自我了斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做傻事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對將要震撼世界的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的存亡不如一葉孤舟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我存在 那這個國家的平衡就會受到影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數人將要流血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將誕生無數被迫母子分離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽嚐人間孤苦的可憐人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣 我還不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能看到我嗎 可能看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 有一隻兔子誤入網中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為美獸會無條件地服從我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就利用那隻兔子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個傻松鼠 不 傻兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒意識到他已經成為人質了 只是想要見到妳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你敢對他下手…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全部取決於妳的回覆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和維多利嘉果然不會就這樣分開的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布羅瓦警部還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能先進去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早點見到維多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我會助你們一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相對 不准任何人碰他一根手指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是妹妹的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我還是要聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子是美獸的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子一死 美獸自然就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利嘉 維多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個不會就此分開的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 把我現在想要的東西給我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是甜點 也不是謎案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想要溫暖的無聊時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.41,0:24:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 快給我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:30.10,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,547)}蒙灰棋局喝將死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【STAFF】
